      "output": "\n\n```sql\nSELECT \n    (SUM(cp.conversions) * (SELECT AVG(o.total_amount) FROM orders o WHERE o.status != 'cancelled') - SUM(cp.spend_usd)) / SUM(cp.spend_usd) AS roi\nFROM campaign_performance cp\nWHERE cp.campaign_id = 5\n```",
